snippet.title: Must Dash Amigos | Xbox One | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience a Loco top-down Battle Racer filled with Piñata Stampedes, Avocados and mayhem for up to 4 Players!

Must Dash Amigos is a humorous, family friendly fun-fest with controls so simple that anyone can play!

To survive in this world you cannot just run; you Must Dash Amigos!

Coming soon to Xbox One!
